♪♪

9
00:01:11,733 --> 00:01:12,800
-Cal!

10
00:01:13,933 --> 00:01:18,233
-What kept you?
-Had to sneak past the old man.

11
00:01:18,367 --> 00:01:19,300
Happy birthday.

12
00:01:19,433 --> 00:01:23,733
♪♪

13
00:01:23,867 --> 00:01:24,700
