♪♪

23
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,100
-[ Giggles ]

24
00:01:57,233 --> 00:02:00,167
-Come on, Ruthie!

25
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,933
Whoo! Whoo!
-[ Chuckles ]

26
00:02:03,067 --> 00:02:08,167
♪♪

27
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:13,600
♪♪

28
